reviewText: I saw him live for free in FLA TWIICE IN OHIO AND PAY  NOW AM GOING TO SEE HIM IN AUG 5TH IN NASHVILLE

Amazon.com I luv'ya.....but with all your wonderful technology can't you please...please list the song titles and performance years on this item. This complaint applies to many other items in the "worlds best and biggest" inventory. Please ..."be the best"!
Has anyone seen this? Is it from the late 60's/early 70's,or is it from the 90's. A song list would be helpful also. Thanks.
